      <title>美元先于就业数据下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-ahead-payrolls-2024-03-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，由于美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔对未来几个月降息更有信心，美元迎来今年最大单周跌幅，而日元则因日本加息的猜测不断升温而上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-ahead-payrolls-2024-03-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 01:12:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚大堡礁遭受严重珊瑚白化</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-great-barrier-reef-suffers-major-coral-bleaching-2024-03-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚政府机构周五表示，澳大利亚大堡礁遭受了重大珊瑚白化事件的袭击，其结果与夏季在生物多样性丰富的地区形成的热应激模式一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-great-barrier-reef-suffers-major-coral-bleaching-2024-03-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 01:10:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港政府公布新国安法草案</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-government-issues-draft-new-national-security-law-2024-03-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港政府周五公布了新的国家安全法草案，一些外国外交官、律师和企业正在仔细审查该文件，因为担心它可能会进一步削弱这个金融中心的自由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-government-issues-draft-new-national-security-law-2024-03-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 00:38:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰推动和平计划，指出朝鲜参与与中国特使的会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-presses-peace-plan-points-n-korean-involvement-talks-with-chinese-envoy-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰高级官员在周四与中国地区特使会面时，敦促基辅结束与俄罗斯长达两年的冲突的计划，并提交了他们所说的朝鲜向莫斯科提供武器的证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-presses-peace-plan-points-n-korean-involvement-talks-with-chinese-envoy-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 23:25:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国陆军情报分析师被控向中国出售军事机密</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-army-intelligence-analyst-charged-with-selling-military-secrets-china-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名美国陆军情报分析员周四被捕，被指控密谋向中国出售敏感国防信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-army-intelligence-analyst-charged-with-selling-military-secrets-china-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 22:10:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝中社称，朝鲜金正恩指导炮兵射击演习</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-guides-artillery-firing-drill-by-korean-peoples-army-kcna-says-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据朝中社周五报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩周四指导了朝鲜人民军的炮兵射击演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-guides-artillery-firing-drill-by-korean-peoples-army-kcna-says-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 21:52:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从骆驼到控制室：印度为大规模的选举活动做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/camels-control-rooms-india-prepares-its-mammoth-election-exercise-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从用驼背将投票机运送到广阔的西部沙漠的偏远角落，到加强监控恶意深度造假的控制室，印度正准备在五月份举行世界上最大规模的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/camels-control-rooms-india-prepares-its-mammoth-election-exercise-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 19:50:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>活动人士称，朝鲜针对 COVID-19 的措施“过于宽泛、过度”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-covid-19-measures-were-overbroad-excessive-activists-say-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国维权人士在一份新报告中表示，朝鲜关闭边境和其他抗疫措施“过于广泛、过度和不必要”，严重影响了粮食安全和基本产品的供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-covid-19-measures-were-overbroad-excessive-activists-say-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 16:03:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国专家小组推迟因阿富汗问题指控布林肯藐视法庭的会议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-panel-postpones-meeting-hold-blinken-contempt-over-afghanistan-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据曾威胁要蔑视布林肯的小组主席透露，国务卿安东尼·布林肯已同意向国会委员会提供其要求的有关 2021 年美国从阿富汗撤军的文件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-panel-postpones-meeting-hold-blinken-contempt-over-afghanistan-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 13:43:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安全负责人表示“不能排除中国干预立陶宛民意调查”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-interference-lithuania-polls-cant-be-ruled-out-says-security-chief-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛反情报部门负责人周四表示，由于立陶宛支持台湾，“绝对不能排除”中国干预今年欧盟和北约成员国立陶宛的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-interference-lithuania-polls-cant-be-ruled-out-says-security-chief-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:31:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
